high_descs: walk over to the counter where the microwave is
open the upper cabinet and take the chalice out
approach the microwave with the chalice
warm the chalice in the microwave then remove
raise the chalice up toward the cabinet above the microwave
put the chalice back in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: get a chalice, warm it in the microwave then put it back where it came from

high_descs: Turn around and face the microwave to the left of the refrigerator.
Open the cabinet door above the microwave and pick up the green wine glass.
Turn to the right and face the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the green glass on the plate to the right of the egg, microwave the glass to warm it up, then open up the microwave, pick up the glass, then close the microwave door.
Move and look up towards the cabinet above the microwave.
Open the cabinet door, place the green wine glass back in the cabinet, and then close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed wine glass in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right go one step then turn right another step and then turn left another step then turn right and go towards the counter.
Open the cabinet in front above the left corner of the microwave.
Pick up the green ice cream cup from the cabinet and close the cabinet then walk one step back turn right one step and then turn left in front of the microwave.
Open the Microwave and put the ice cream cup into the microwave then turn on the microwave and when cooking is done open the microwave again and take out the cup.
Take the cup higher to the cabinet above the microwave and open the cabinet.
Put the cup into the cabinet and close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Cook the Ice cream cup and put it in the cabinet.
